### POSTS API (Developer 1)
### ----------------------------------------------------------------

### 1. Add a New Post 
POST {{baseUrl}}/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "My First Post",
    "content": "This is the content of the post.",
    "userId": "{{userId}}"
}

### 2. Get All Posts 
GET {{baseUrl}}/post

### 3. Get a Post by ID 
GET {{baseUrl}}/post/{{postId}}

### 4. Get Posts by User 
GET {{baseUrl}}/post?userId={{userId}}

### 5. Update a Post 
PUT {{baseUrl}}/post/{{postId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Updated Title",
    "content": "Updated content here.",
    "userId": "{{userId}}"
}

 